</s>
<s id="1300:5" video="http://amelia.sslmit.unibo.it/video/video.php?id=1300&start=00.00.55&end=00.01.09">
Currently it 's not satisfactory and this is a good ... time for us to it 's good for e- European patients to look to something which is based on needs , not based on economic pow- wealth and obligations .
